# Tetra

 *Tetra* is a simple application that was made to test my [3D engine](https://github.com/pedroth/Learning/tree/master/src/main/java/windowThreeDim), it lets you see some **triangular meshes**. It can also generate random **planets**.

Press `h` for help. Feel free to download the program below.

